rosoft Bing logo is...]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Google Home's new script editor can make smart device automations even more powerful]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>谷歌上个月发布了<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/googles-redesigned-home-app-is-available-to-everyone-185733317.html">重新设计的 Home 应用程序</a>，增加了例程，让用户可以更好地控制智能家居自动化。现在，它正在引入一个新的脚本编辑器，该公司在<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.googlenestcommunity.com/t5/Blog/Create-powerful-automations-with-our-new-script-editor-now-available-in/ba-p/433461">Google Nest 博客文章</a>中宣布。它为用户提供了对自动化的更精细控制，让他们可以做诸如“天黑后客厅电视打开时调暗灯光和拉下百叶窗”之类的事情，引用谷歌的一个例子。不过，它确实需要一些基本的编程能力，因为它使用 YAML 数据序列化语言。</p><p>构建自动化需要三个要素：启动器、条件和操作。启动器触发自动化，例如在上面的示例中打开电视。同时，条件是脚本运行前必须满足的先决条件；例如时间必须在日落和日出之间。最后，动作指定随后将触发哪些设备，即放下百叶窗和关灯。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/ae8aaff0-0a9a-11ee-bfdf-6ec790dab1c5" style="height:1013px;width:1600px;" alt="Google Home 的新脚本编辑器可以让智能家居自动化更加强大" data-uuid="94587b1b-7eb0-333f-8be6-61523e22aa32"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">谷歌</div></figure><p>虽然 Google 已经提供了相当程度的例程控制，但您无法执行诸如在自动化或设置条件下对多个启动器进行编程之类的操作。相比之下，脚本编辑器允许使用近 100 个可用于创建自定义自动化的启动器、条件和操作。</p><p>脚本编辑器可在 Google Home 应用程序的公共预览版或网络上使用，以及各种 <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://developers.home.google.com/automations/example-scripts">示例脚本自动化</a>。谷歌也提供了<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://developers.home.google.com/codelabs/create-a-scripted-automation#0">分步指南</a>。它适用于 Google Home 和第三方智能家居设备，自动化可与流行的传感器（包括 Matter 支持的传感器）配合使用。有关更多信息，请查看<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.googlenestcommunity.com/t5/Blog/Create-powerful-automations-with-our-new-script-editor-now-available-in/ba-p/433461">Google Nest 博客</a>。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/google-homes-new-script-editor-can-make-smart-device-automations-even-more-powerful-103019126.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/google-homes-new-script-editor-can-make-smart-device-automations-even-more-powerful-103019126.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8bc72a6c-68f8-4500-88b8-7c964edac04a</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 14 Jun 2023 10:30:19 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686738621</ingested><modified> 2023-06-14T10:30:23+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="900" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/4af052a0-0a96-11ee-8f3f-f927c7cea35c" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="900" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/4af052a0-0a96-11ee-8f3f-f927c7cea35c" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Google Home's new script editor can make smart home automations even more powerful]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Google Home's new script editor can make smart home automations even more powerful]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[McDonald's just released a Grimace Game Boy Color game]]></title><description type="html"><![CDA